data.description: GREAT SOUTH TAMPA HOME THAT IS NEWER & HAS CONTEMPORARY INTERIOR WITH OPEN FLOOR PLAN & VAULTED CEILINGS. This home features a split bedroom plan w/ a complete master suite & two other large bedrooms. Nice size kitchen which opens out to large greatroom that is a dining room/living room combination great for entertaining. French doors lead out to large 21x13 covered lanai that has brick pavers and a screened enclosure. The inside utility room is next to the kitchen and has side entrance to parking pad, great for unloading groceries.   Garagew is air conditioned for that man cave you've always wanted. The kitchen includes all appliances, including plenty of counter space for any gourmet cook. There are ceramic tile and laminated wood floors in the living areas and carpet that is less than one year old in the bedrooms. Home is ready to move in. Comes with $600 Home Warranty included.
